                        Urnaultrices quis curabitur phasellentesque congue magnis vestibulum</p>

                </div>

                <div class="main-about__list">

                    {% set mainAboutList = ["Low prices","Guarantees","Without intermediaries","Work on the market for more than 5 years"] %}
                    {% for i in 0..3 %}
                    <div>

                        <h6 class="h6">{{ mainAboutList[i] }}</h6>
                        <p>Welcome to a place filled with life, yet removed from the bustle and congestion of the city.
                            A place to see a movie with the family</p>

                    </div>
                    {% endfor %}

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="section-guid" style="background-image:url('./img/bg/main-guid-bg.png')">

        <div class="wrapper">

            <div class="main-guid" id="guid">

                <div class="main-guid__text">

                    <div class="h1">GUIDE</div>

                    <p>Travel packages for every budget. Which one is yours?Nullamlacus dui ipsum conseque loborttis non euisque morbi penas dapibulum orna. Urnaultrices quis curabitur phasellentesque congue magnis vestibulum quismodo nulla et feugiat adipiscinia pellentum leo.Travel packages for every budget. Which one is yours?</p>

                    <div class="main-guid__slogan">

                        <p data-quot="&ldquo;">As a head, smart people will open a guidebook!As a head, smart people will open a guidebook!</p>

                    </div>

                    <div class="main-guid__button">
                        <a href="" class="button-green">open all tours</a>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <div class="main-guid__list">

                    {% for item in guidList %}
                    <div class="main-guid__item">

                        <a href="./guid.html" data-anchor="{{ item.id }}" style="background-image:url('./img/guid-item.png')">

                            <img src="./img/icon/guid-icon-{{ loop.index0 % 5 + 1 }}.png" alt="">

                            <p>{{ item.text }}</p>

                        </a>

                    </div>
                    {% endfor %}

                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

    <section class="section-blog" style="background-image:url('./img/bg/block-bg.png')">

        <div class="wrapper">

            <div class="main-blog">

                <div class="main-blog__text">

                    <div class="h1">Blog</div>
